original_title: Eintracht Frankfurt - Eine Traumreise durch Europa
overview: 42 years after winning the UEFA Cup, Eintracht Frankfurt is making Europa League history again. The players, the coach and those responsible take us on their emotional journey through Europe. Tens of thousands of fans followed them through these unforgettable games to the final in Seville. And the voices of the reporters made the grandiose football moments audible. They all have their say in Eintracht Frankfurt's journey through Europe.
title: Eintracht Frankfurt - a dream trip through Europe
